- Modify journal_read to verify that the value of recnum is sequential.

- Modify journal_read to write data from transactions to (invisible)
  temporary files, and spawn the processes with these files as standard
  input only after the end of the transaction could be read.

- Modify journal_read to wait for new records to be output to the
  "current" file.

- Modify the file format to align transaction starts on block boundaries.

